                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970920-36-defend289 t17970920-36-punish187"></join>
               fined 50l
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Raftey, <rs id="t17970920-36-verdict188" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970920-36-verdict188" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first London Jury, before The LORD CHIEF BARON.</p>
